Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.82,0:00:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡岡崎君 請跟我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 你一定很困擾對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然聽到這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不說出來我會很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們也才剛認識不久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然經常有跟杏三個人一起吃吃飯什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.53,0:00:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是說我討厭你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是說從沒當作戀愛對象看待過呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 這種說法很失禮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣也不介意的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要試著交往看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們接下來會逐漸瞭解對方的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.90,0:01:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我覺得接下來的時間不是作為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.46,0:01:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是作為男女朋友來度過的話可能也不壞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起你就是我的女朋友了 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 眼淚 控制不住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是做夢一樣 好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的志願是護士學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 那是我從小的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對將來的事完全沒考慮過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我認為不用著急
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行 如果整天遊手好閒的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會被你討厭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事絕不可能發生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼事 我都不會討厭岡崎君的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為還從沒有人對我說過這樣的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有點感動了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:03:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 杏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大好的星期天你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好陪在椋身邊怎麼行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 別瞎操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從二年級開始就一直喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你覺得你們能好好發展下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該能行吧 她既認真又溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉動不動就紅 所以稍微讓人有點擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯 不過她的這種地方也很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:05:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 你可真是什麼事都想著妹妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不盡是如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟椋接過吻了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？ 才 才沒做過那種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行 你要更主動一些才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說… 我可是第一次跟女生交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要練習一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就把我當成椋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是雙胞胎 感覺上也很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是練習 真親了可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你剛才當真了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你個及格分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是在那公園裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡崎不就是那個不良少年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是那兩人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們原來是同班 而且現在關係似乎也很不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 噓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎樣也不能在那種地方 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道就沒一點羞恥感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好啊 岡崎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼連你也這樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？ 我跟杏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.81,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在走廊裡跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經傳遍整個學校了 說你昨天跟杏接了吻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 不 那個該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那麼一回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢 我也覺得你最近不太正常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不說了我沒做過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說跟我交往的是她妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？ 你跟藤林椋？ 真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼意外嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們倆性格完全不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是杏的話我倒還能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便下結論
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這傳聞藤林估計也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正只要在學校就算不想聽也會傳進耳朵裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在這兒在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微陪我一下 不會浪費你太多時間的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛… 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可什麼也沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 說實話確實是難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊 我所說的話就那麼奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 一直以來不是從來都沒有過這種感覺嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是那個吧 因為過於接近而無法察覺的心意？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 讓你見識一下顯而易見的證據吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很奇怪啊 你真的喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說錯了的話我向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 你應該是喜歡岡崎的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 想消除自己跟你的流言才想跟我交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流言什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是流言的話 何必做到這種地步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 陽平說過的話你可別當真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著你跟椋關係那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想著「我也交個男朋友多好」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就想乾脆就找陽平好了 於是就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道因為這麼簡單的理由就去找男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是多管什麼閒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要想著椋的事就行了 知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓女朋友擔心的男人最差勁了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共八百日元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想試著叫叫你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 像杏還不是直呼我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 都已經是這種關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:11:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不介意的話也叫我椋好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋 朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天…見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去春原那兒好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牡丹？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可是星期天 沒人會來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牡丹 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 你不是跟椋去約會了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都完全濕透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要想著椋的事就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟你是椋的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在跟這些沒關係吧 你會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要管我 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就別再管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別對我這麼溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個笨蛋 你對我溫柔的話我會誤會的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕 害怕去告白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果向你告白 被拒絕了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許就連朋友也做不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果和你交往了 又會讓椋傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 還不如放棄了好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只有這樣才不會有人受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 我現在心裡滿是後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是笨呢 明明是自己已經決定了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:13:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是藤林杏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是椋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也的確是個難題呢 在雙胞胎之間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你 會怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我站在你的立場上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還有什麼好說的 自然是兩人都要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以把你揍到爬不起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過說真的 確實是很難辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣乾脆…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想跟雙方都保持距離的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就真是個極品廢柴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 想讓自己一直保持清白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然事已至此 無論怎樣你都會傷害其中一方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你越晚給出答案 傷害就會越深
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你們三人中的任何一人都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便 我能再說一句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的煩惱太奢侈了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 覓食了覓食了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟我說的是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我們兩個人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是漫畫的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人獨處在放學後的教室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會接吻什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要用姓稱呼我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…一直想著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想輸給姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐一直在注視著誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明知道 卻仍然去找姐姐商量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我想跟朋也君搞好關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:17:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐雖然很吃驚 但還是馬上笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說包在她身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明知道她會那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也知道自己很卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我也想待在朋也君身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不能替代姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會變得像姐姐一樣主動的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會留長頭髮 也會學習做料理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會成為朋也君心儀的女生的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望你做那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想待在朋也君身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤林…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 請假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 鈴木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你交往的那些日子我真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:19:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次明白被人需要是多麼開心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想就這樣一直跟你好好相處下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了一件最差勁的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有了你 卻還想著別人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我注意到這事後 也沒有告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我利用了你的溫柔 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你的頭髮…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椋跟我說「不要逃避」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想著一直這樣下去就好了 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜傷害椋也要選擇你 這樣卑鄙的事我不想做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她卻說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「這是不可能的」 「已經太晚了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果真的喜歡朋也 就不能再逃避了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我們不管怎樣 總是會有人受到傷害的」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「畢竟我們喜歡上了同一個人」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在一定在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.21,0:20:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的是…太晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是覺察 矇混 還是面對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這將是最後一次傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是那孩子 我 還是朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你 朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都喜歡著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果接受你的道歉 原諒了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓我感覺這全都是假的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把那段時光當作珍貴的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是開心的事 悲傷的事 所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:21:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 請你不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天啊 要去哪兒來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.63,0:22:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了要去玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉 那個取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為難得椋說想去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.45,0:22:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近可真是熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 我真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會不會覺得還是跟椋在一起更舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.53,0:22:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 我可要生氣了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.71,0:22:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣我才能稍微安心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是有點扭曲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更直接了當一點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.49,0:23:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.99,0:23:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
